name: Just Bruneians
description:
@vanilliyy | This art sparked the #justbruneians movement in 2019 - it  brought together Brunei’s creative community to share the same frustration towards the negative connotation: “They’re Just Bruneians”.   There are so many Bruneians that deserve to be noticed for their passion, skill and creativity. Possessing creative talents is something to be respected and admired. Possessing creative talent is also something you should be proud of.
@justbruneians
